Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:16.71,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't underestimate me. I'm still an instructor.}Nepodceňuj mě. Stále jsem instruktorem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.46,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Where are you, Tsubaki-chan?!}Kde jsi Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.12,Shinsou - Text,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Here, Kotecchan!}Tady, Kotíku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.54,Shinsou - Text,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki wins!}Tsubaki vyhrává!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:35.15,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{This was all I could come up with.}To bylo vše, co jsem mohl udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.17,Shinsou - Text,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Not bad.}Není to špatné.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.68,Shinsou - Text,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{That's enough, Haru!}To stačí, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.81,Shinsou - Text,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Not bad, Akira.}Není to špatné, Akiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.02,Shinsou - Text,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe I'll go all out, too!}Možná, že do toho taky dám všechno!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.91,Shinsou - Text,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{It would've been nice to run\N with you more, Akira.}Bylo by pěkné, kdybych s tebou mohl být déle, Akiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:12.96,Shinsou - Text,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry, Haru...}Promiň, Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.97,Shinsou - Text,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't beat Chiyu.}Nemůžeš porazit Chiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.10,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Cut the bullshit!}Dost těch keců.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:27.87,Shinsou - Text,CHIYU,0000,0000,0000,,{And in the end, it was just as planned.}A nakonec to dopadlo, tak jak jsem plánovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.57,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{We've always been broken.}Vždy jsme byli zlomeni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.74,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Nationalist dog!}Vládní pse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.83,Shinsou - Text,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{You're just a mutt sniffing around, yourself.}Furt se jen plížíš kolem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:01.37,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Not bad. I'm impressed.}Není to špatné. Jsem ohromen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.18,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{You're as strong as ever.}Vůbec ses nezměnil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.89,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{That hurts.}To zabolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:10.52,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry. Looks like we both need healing.}Promiň. Vypadá to, že oba se potřebujeme vyléčit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.90,Shinsou - Text,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Listen to your requiem.}Poslechni si svůj rekviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.49,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't hold back!}Nebudu se držet zpátky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.41,Shinsou - Text,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{You've wronged your country!}Ublížili jste vlastní zemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.71,Shinsou - Text,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Suruga!}Surugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.67,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry. Did that hurt?}Promiň. Bolelo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:49.77,Shinsou - Text,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The death god's scythe reaches all.}Kosa boha smrti dosáhne všech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.05,Shinsou - Text,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{A secret arrow.}Skrytý šíp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.90,Shinsou - Text,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I see...}Chápu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.59,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Was this the only way?}Byla to jediná možnost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:12.64,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Fate is a shadowy figure.}Osud je stínová postava.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.13,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Chase after it, and it runs.\N Run, and it chases you.}Pronásledujete to, a utíkáte. Utíkáte a zase vás pronásleduje.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.76,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Are we evil?}Jsme zlí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:23.51,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Who knows? I certainly don't.}Kdo ví? Já určitě ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.58,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Can we correct this twisted fate?}Můžeme tento překroucený osud zvrátit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.18,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know.}Nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.21,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.85,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun.}Chihiro.
