Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.74,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, come on.}Ale, no tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.05,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You keep going for the}Pořád opakuješ {\i1}{kote}kote{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.32,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Go for the}Přejdi na {\i1}{men}men{\i0}{ Chihiro-san.}, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.54,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{A win is a win, Kotetsu.}Vítězství je vítězství, Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:04.21,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Complaining about a loss\Nreveals your immaturity.}Stěžování si na prohru dokazuje tvou nezralost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.37,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Dad.}Tati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.81,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the mystery of non-killing.}Je to tajemství nezabíjení.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.93,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Stealing your opponent's\Nstrength and using it to win}Ukrást nepřítelovu sílu a použít ji k vítězství
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.04,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{is the greatest essence of swordplay.}je největší podstatou šermu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:18.73,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{In a real battle, you won't be able to\N defeat your opponents with}V reálné bitvě nebudete moci porazit své soupeře {\i1}kote{\i0} {strikes.}úderem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.69,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I know.}Já vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.87,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go again, Chihiro-san.}Pojďme znovu, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.57,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry. I have to get ready.}Promiň. Musím se připravit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.23,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{No fair! You're just quitting after you win?}To není fér. Končíš hned potom co vyhraješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.16,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You don't want breakfast?}Nebudeš chtít snídani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.04,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know what to do with him.}Nevím, co s ním dělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:45.88,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{If only he'd change his mind,\N I could live in easy retirement.}Kdyby jen změnil názor, mohl bych žít v poklidném důchodu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.66,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Your rolled omelets are the best, Chihiro-san.}Tvoje omelety jsou nejlepší, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.21,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't live without them, Kotetsu.}Nedokážeš bez nich žít, Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.18,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{They're so fluffy...}Jsou tak nadýchané...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.97,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I know. You stirred them a hundred times, right?}Vím. Ty jsi je stokrát rozmíchal, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.45,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The secret is watching the heat\Nand not stirring too much.}Tajemství je v sledování teplotě a nemíchání moc dlouho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.47,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't need to know that. I just eat.}Nepotřebuji to vědět. Právě jím.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.69,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You should at least learn to cook.}Mohl by ses naučit vařit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.59,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? I've got you.}Proč? Mám tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.59,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What am I, your wife?}Co jsem, tvoje žena?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.98,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, why not?}Jo, proč ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.76,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{We'll take over the dojo together.}Převezmeme dojo společně.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.97,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll be the instructor, \Nand I'll be your assistant.}Ty budeš instruktor a já tvůj asistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.86,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you think, Dad?}Co myslíš tati?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.67,Shinsou - Text,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{I prefer hot spring eggs.}Mám radši horké jarní vejce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.33,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not what I'm asking.}To není to, na co se ptám.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.26,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Then we'll have hot spring eggs tomorrow.}Potom, zítra uděláme nějaké horké jarní vejce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.42,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{If we're going to be instructors,}Pokud budeme instruktory,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.06,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{we'll have to be good \Nexamples to our students.}musíme být dobrým příkladem pro naše studenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:53.20,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll need to show them how strong you are.}Musíš jim ukázat jak silný jsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.22,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Get a good}Udělej dobrý {\i1}men{\i0} {hit in.}úder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.57,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're stronger than me in matches.}Jsi v zápasech silnější než já.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.75,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh? I'm strong?}Hm? Já a silný?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.58,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Seriously?}Opravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.81,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I've never beaten you, though.}Nikdy jsem tě neporazil, pokud vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.50,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san, are you really leaving?}Opravdu odcházíš, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.30,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, I guess.}Jo, asi jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.68,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why? What's there to complain about?}Proč? Co ti vadí?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.43,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't have any complaints.}Nic mi nevadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:26.62,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Since you took me in, I've felt nothing\Nbut gratitude for you and your father.}" Od chvíle, kdy jste si mě vzali, necítil jsem nic než vděčnost vůči vám. "
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.85,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{He raised me until now.\N He even sent me to college.}Vedl mě až dosud. Dokonce mě poslal na vysokou školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.15,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But...}Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.45,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{But what?}Ale co?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.45,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{"To be or not to be."}"Být či nebýt"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.23,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Shakespeare again?}Zase Shakespeare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.46,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Answer the question, Chihiro-san.}Odpověz na otázku, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.81,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I shouldn't have told you.}Neměl jsem ti to říkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.41,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm just thinking about it for now.}Jen o tom přemýšlím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.21,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What's going to happen to the dojo?}Co se stane s dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.17,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that why?}To je ten důvod?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.00,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I knew there was some reason\N you were so persistent today.}Věděl jsem, že existuje nějaký důvod, proč jsi dnes tak vytrvalý.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.32,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, but...}Jo, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.72,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I haven't decided yet.}Ještě jsem se nerozhodl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.48,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't tell your dad.}Neříkej to tvému otci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.59,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.92,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.18,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Iku-san, good morning.}Dobré ráno, Iku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.20,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{We have first period free.}Máme první hodinu volnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.76,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go to the cafeteria.}Pojďme do jídelny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.89,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{We ate already.}Už jsme jedli.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.70,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{Well, I haven't!}No, já ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.44,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{They serve ginger-fried pork\Non Thursday mornings, right?} Ve čtvrtek ráno podávají smažené vepřové se zázvorem, že jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.08,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{I always eat here.}Vždycky jsem tu jedl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.27,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sounds like a heavy breakfast.}Zní to jako těžká snídaně.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.26,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Okay, I'm in!}Ok, jsem pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.05,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You already ate.}Ty už si jedl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.42,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{We're the only ones with first period off.}Jsme jediní, kdo mají první hodinou volnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.87,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{Go to class, first-year.}Jděte do třídy, prváci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.84,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't be mean, Senpai.}Tak se nezlob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.76,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this?}Co to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.94,Shinsou - Text,IKURO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm covering my ears, but I can still hear it.}Kryju si uši, ale i tak to slyším.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.36,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.37,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{C-Chihiro-san...}C-Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.88,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.33,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Hang in there!}Vydrž!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.83,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{That sound...}Ten zvuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.83,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{"We are such stuff as dreams are made on."}" Jsme stvořeni z toho, co tvoří sny. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.07,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{"Yea, all which it inherit, shall dissolve,}Jo, všechno, co to zdědí, se rozloží.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.54,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{And, like this insubstantial pageant faded,}A jak, tenhle nepodstatný živý obraz zmizel,...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.61,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Leave not a rack behind."}Nenech za sebou vůbec nic. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.90,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{The Tempest}{\i0}{, huh?}Bouře, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.75,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Which means this is all a dream.}Což znamená, že je to všechno jen sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:35.75,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Fate, continuously woven from a thread\N of intertwining good and evil.}Osud, neustále tkané z nití prolínání dobra a zla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.43,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you trying to say?}Co se tím snažíš říct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.65,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you like it?}Nelíbí se ti to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.20,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{They're all words that are inside you.}Jsou to všechna slova, která jsou uvnitř tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.04,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Even theater can be a killjoy\N if it's taken too far.}Dokonce i zábavné divadlo může krachnout, když se zajde moc daleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:52.13,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I like Shakespeare, but\NI don't like seeing it twisted so.}Mám rád Shakespeara, ale nerad vidím jak je překrucován.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.14,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Man of vermilion.}Rumělkový muž.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.27,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Heroic power resides in your blood.}Hrdinská síla spočívá v tvé krvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:03.91,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The king imprisoned on a desert island\Nin a distant sea puts his subjects to work,}Král uvězněn na pustém ostrově v dalekém moři žene své poddané do práce
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.20,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{continuously searching for answers.}a hledá odpovědi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.91,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you talking about?}O čem to mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.40,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are you?}Kdo jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.63,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I am Dux.}Já jsem Dux.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.22,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Until the end of time,}Až do konce času,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:22.18,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{we will repeat this heroic\Nscene again and again}budeme opakovat tuto hrdinskou scénu znovu a znovu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.81,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{in the words of nations not yet known.}ve slovech národů, které nejsou dosud známy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.19,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Inuki, he's awake!}Inuki, probral se!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.64,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{The Sleeping Prince is finally awake.}Spící princ se konečně vzbudil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.49,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you give him a magic kiss?}Dala si mu kouzelný polibek?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.62,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah, right!}Jo, jasně!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.36,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm joking.}Jen vtipkuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.53,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Check his consciousness levels.}Zkontroluj jeho úroveň vědomí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.79,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, hot stuff.}Hej, hezoune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.25,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the last one.}Jsi poslední.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.55,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Do you know who you are?}Víš kdo jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.58,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I... I...}Já... já...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:06.66,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't tell me you have amnesia.}Neříkej mi, že jsi ztratil paměť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.05,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.09,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm Kamina Chihiro.}Jsem Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.18,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Okay, good.}Ok, dobrý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.56,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what the student ID you had says, too.}To samé říká i jeho studentská karta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.14,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Jokei University second-year\Nstudent, English department...}Univerzita Jokei, student druhého ročníku katedry angličtiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.39,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{What happened to me—}Co se mi to stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.71,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't interrupt!}Nepřerušuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.59,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what you call impolite.}To je to, čemu říkáte nezdvořilost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.53,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't hit the patient. That's also impolite.}Nemlať pacienta. To je taky nezdvořilé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.53,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Shut up.}Sklapni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.95,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Where are we?}Kde to jsme?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.64,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{The Jokei University hospital.}Jokeiská univerzitní nemocnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.96,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm the attending physician, Akaya Inuki.}Jsem doktor, Akaya Inuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.24,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{This is Sakiyama Koume.}Tohle je Sakiyama Koume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.84,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't call me a "this."}Nenazývej mě " tohle "
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:47.87,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{So, Sleeping Prince, you've\Nbeen asleep for five months.}Tak, spící princi, spal si přes pět měsíců.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.35,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you know that?}Víš o tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.65,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Five months?! You can't be serious.}Pět měsíců?! To nemůžete myslet vážně.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:55.67,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Most people woke up within a week.}Většina lidí se probudila do týdne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.17,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Now, what did you dream about?}Tak, o čem si snil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.31,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Dream?}Snil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.86,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Dreams of another world.}Sen o jiném světě.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.80,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Dreams in which you became something else.}Sen, ve kterém si se stal něčím jiným.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.90,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Something else?}Něčím jiným?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.11,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Um, what are you talking about?}O čem to mluvíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:14.16,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{A lot of people mentioned it after they\N lost consciousness in the Great Collapse.}Mnoho lidí se o tom zmínilo, po Velkém zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.12,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{"The Great Collapse?"}"Velké zhroucení?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.87,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{It'd be quicker for you to see for yourself.}Bylo by rychlejší to vidět.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.31,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this?}Co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.00,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Tokyo after the Great Collapse.}Tokyo po Velkém zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.88,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this Great Collapse?}Co je to Velké zhroucení?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:47.12,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{You must've heard that strange\N sound before you collapsed.}Musel jsi slyšet ten divný zvuk, než jsi zkolaboval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:51.15,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{We still don't know what it was.}Stále nevíme co to bylo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.97,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{When we woke up, that giant plant had grown}Když jsme se probrali, tak už obří rostlina vyrostla
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.88,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{and we were enveloped in a red mist.}a byli jsme obklopeni rudou mlhou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:04.46,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{We have no way of knowing what \Nhappened during that week.}Nemůžeme vědět, co se stalo během toho týdne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.84,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the Great Collapse.}To je Velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.40,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is that plant?}Co je to za rostlinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.39,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened to Tokyo?!}Co se stalo s Tokyem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.76,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, shut up!}Ah, sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:18.22,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{It's too difficult to explain.\N Ask your friend about it.}Je to těžké vysvětlit. Zeptej se svého přítele.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.95,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You can come in now.}Můžete vejít.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.02,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank goodness! I'm so glad you're okay!}Díky bohu. Jsem tak rád, že jsi v pořádku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.89,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{They wouldn't let me see you.}Nechtěli mě k tobě pustit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.18,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Your nurse is astoundingly rude, too.}Tvoje sestra je neuvěřitelně hrubá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.66,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{What was that?}Co to mělo být, sakra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.99,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{If they'd dissected you,}Kdyby tě rozpitvali,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.85,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I swore I'd avenge you before\N committing ritual suicide.}Přísahal jsem, že tě pomstím, než bych spáchal rituální sebevraždu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.83,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{What era are you from, exactly?}Z jaké doby přesně jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.02,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{He's always like this.}Je takový vždycky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.09,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{He's been underfoot every day.}Jenom se pořád plete pod nohy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.42,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry. You must've been worried.}Promiň. Musel sis dělat starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.65,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm surprised I can walk.}Překvapuje mě, že mohu chodit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:01.27,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Everyone who passed out during the \NGreat Collapse is surprisingly healthy.}Každý, kdo omdlel během Velkého zhroucení je překvapivě zdravý.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.85,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I couldn't believe I'd been asleep for a week.}Nemohl jsem uvěřit, že jsem spal týden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.74,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Congratulations on your\N recovery, Kamina Chihiro-kun.}Gratuluji ti k uzdravení, Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.94,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san.}Pane Kakiharo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.99,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you doing here?}Co tu děláte?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.45,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Journalists have a keen nose.}Novináři mají citlivý nos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:23.50,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{"Post-Great Collapse, the last\Ncomatose individual finally awakes."}Po Velkém zhroucení se konečně probouzí poslední jednotlivec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.96,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There's the headline.}To je titulek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.17,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why were you asleep for five months?}Proč si spal pět měsíců?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.01,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey!}Hele!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.98,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you not bring enough people down with you?}Nepřinesl sis více lidí sebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:35.51,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Or is it no fun unless you kill them yourself?}Nebo to není zábava dokud je nezabiješ sám?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.47,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Like you did 13 years ago.}Jako před třinácti lety.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.60,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's enough!}To stačí!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.72,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Why are you always following\N Chihiro-san around?}Proč všude Chihira sledujete?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.23,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You make it sound bad. It's my job.}Takhle to zní hrozně. Je to moje práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.13,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll leave it at that,}Nechám to tak,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:55.04,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{including the truth about\N what happened 13 years ago.}včetně pravdy o tom, co se stalo před 13 lety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.00,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{So scary.}Děsivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.61,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go, Tsubasa.}Jdeme, Tsubaso.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:11.54,Shinsou - Text - Italic,NEWS,0000,0000,0000,,{Five months after the Great Collapse,\N"Save Tokyo" demonstrations}Pět měsíců po Velkém zhroucení se v hlavním městě Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:15.41,Shinsou - Text - Italic,NEWS,0000,0000,0000,,{are being held in the capital of Osaka.}konají demonstrace "Zachraňte Tokyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.28,Shinsou - Text - Italic,NEWS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{The government is sending\N trillions of yen in food}Vláda utratí za jídlo tři miliardy yenů
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:23.43,Shinsou - Text - Italic,NEWS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{and medical assistance to the special\N autonomous district of Tokyo,}a lékařskou pomoc pro zvláštní autonomní čtvrť v Tokyu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.52,sign_24936_238_What_will_happen,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{What will happen to Tokyo?!}Co se stane s Tokyem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.52,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Special autonomous district?}Speciální autonomní čtvrť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.94,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what they're calling Tokyo now.}To je to, jak říkají teď Tokyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.86,Shinsou - Text - Italic,NEWS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{however, many issues still remain...}stále však zůstává mnoho otázek ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.04,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{No one can get out because of the red mist.}Nikdo se nemůže dostat pryč kvůli rudé mlze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.30,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you mean?}Co tím myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.27,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the red mist.}Tohle je rudá mlha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.03,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Can you see it?}Vidíš ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:40.44,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{There are colonies all over the place,\N but it encompasses all of Tokyo.}Jsou tam všude kolonie, ale obklopuje to celé Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.50,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Red mist...}Rudá mlha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:48.42,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I heard you could get in and out at first, but...}Slyšel jsem, že by ses mohl dostat dovnitř a ven první, ale ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.88,Shinsou - Text,DRIVER,0000,0000,0000,,{Now everyone stays away.}Teď se všichni drží stranou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:54.55,Shinsou - Text,DRIVER,0000,0000,0000,,{They say no one's been able\N to pass through the red mist.}Říkají, že nikdo nebyl schopen projít přes rudou mlhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.55,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{It was already like this\N by the time I woke up.}Už to tak bylo, když jsem se probudil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.80,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{There was a lot of confusion.}Bylo to velmi matující.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.48,Shinsou - Text,DRIVER,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't leave,}Nemůžeš odejít,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.44,Shinsou - Text,DRIVER,0000,0000,0000,,{but the power and water's flowing.}ale proud i voda fungují.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.16,Shinsou - Text,DRIVER,0000,0000,0000,,{Home's where you make it.}Domov je tam, kde si ho uděláš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.28,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.37,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You just got out of the hospital.}Sotva si opustil nemocnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.61,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You should sleep until we get home.}Měl by ses vyspat až dorazíme domů.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.82,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're right.}Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.66,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll do that.}To udělám.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.70,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The dojo?}Dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.55,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this?}Co to má být?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.09,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Sir!}Pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.71,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What was that?}Co to bylo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:44.58,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you okay?}Jsi v pořádku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.35,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.35,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{How's your dad?}Jak se má tvůj otec?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.35,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{My dad? He's doing great.}Můj táta? Daří se mu dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.45,sign_27362_269_Domyoji_Dojo,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Domyoji Dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.14,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You're finally home.}Konečně jsi doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.42,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I feel strange.}Cítím se divně.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.08,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's like I just left this morning.}Je to jako bych odešel ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.46,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{This sound...}Ten zvuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.66,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this?}Co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.47,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{My body feels hot...}Celé moje tělo hoří.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.21,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is he making this sound?}On dělá ten zvuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.52,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Dad?}Tati?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.44,Shinsou - Text,KAZAMA,0000,0000,0000,,{Run!}Utíkej!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.64,Shinsou - Text,KAZAMA,0000,0000,0000,,{The instructor...}Instruktor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.76,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that... your dad?}To je... tvůj otec?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.95,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Dammit, what's going on?!}Sakra, o co tu jde?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.52,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:02.37,Shinsou - Text - Italic,RAKAN,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't defeat your\N opponents with}Nemůžeš svého protivníka porazit {\i0}kote{\i1} {strikes.}úderem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.03,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
